# insertedModelsArray

**Instance Property**

The array of inserted models that the context is yet to persist.

## Declaration

```swift
var insertedModelsArray: [any PersistentModel] { get }
```

## Inserting models

- **insert(_:)**: Registers the specified model with the context so it can include the model in the next save operation.
